author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: The COMME des GARÇONS x NikeLab Air VaporMax Re-Releases Tomorrow
text:
Visit the original post to see all 2 images from this gallery. 
Brand: NikeLab, COMME des GARÇONS
Model: Air VaporMax
Key Features: Flyknit upper, air bubble cushioning system, sock-like collar, co-branding.
Release Date: March 25, 2017
Price: Expect the sneaker to retail for $190 USD, falling in line with Nike’s in-house VaporMax releases.
Availability: Dover Street Market New York , CDG New York shop in Chelsea.
Editor’s Notes: Following up on a limited release in February , the white COMME des GARÇONS x NikeLab Air VaporMax will once again be made available tomorrow, March 25. As can be expected, the futuristic Air Max model should fly off the shelves in a hurry.
The white Comme des Garçons x Nike VaporMax arrive tomorrow Saturday 25th March at Dover Street Market New York. @nike Also arriving at CDG New York shop in Chelsea
